61#define ASN1_MALLOC_ENCODE(T, B, BL, S, L, R) \
62 do { \
63 (BL) = length_##T((S)); \
64 (B) = malloc((BL)); \
65 if((B) == NULL) { \
66 (R) = ENOMEM; \
67 } else { \
68 (R) = encode_##T(((unsigned char*)(B)) + (BL) - 1, (BL), \
69 (S), (L)); \
70 if((R) != 0) { \
71 free((B)); \
72 (B) = NULL; \
73 } \
74 } \
75 } while (0)
